Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想要什么 洛可？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What do you want, Rocco?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人们希望的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What we all want.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是不想死得早 死得穷 死得孤独\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To not die young, poor or alone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}曼尼\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Manny...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些家伙…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These guys, they...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我不交出他们想要的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I don't give them what they're after,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们会杀了我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they'll kill me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别动 洛可\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hold it, Rocco.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我们不跟那些家伙作对\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We don't fight these guys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或许你能…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sure, maybe you get that...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 烦 讨厌 - 卡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Shit. God damn it. - Cut!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 各位\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sorry, everyone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们再来一次 艾迪 我不知道发生了什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're going again, Eddie. I don't know what happened.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起 山姆\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sorry, Sam.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偏偏在编剧来的时候出糗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Of course, the one day the author is among us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然他来了 但我们跟他不是一伙的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Among us. Sure as hell ain't one of us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的精彩台词是什么 特朗勃？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What's my brilliant line, Trumbo?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我正好拿在手上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh! I've got it right here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"或许你能如愿活得长长久久"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"sure, maybe you get that long, happy life we all want."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:03:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你要我对抗什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, what do you got me fighting for then?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家和平共处 友善待人嘛\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, peace on Earth. Good will toward men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没这回事 这里可是美国\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, you can't do that. This is America.{\r}
