Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们不顾一切只为追求正义\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Whatever it takes to seek justice!{\r}
