Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这次我绝不会越线过去你的阵营\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And I won't cross your picket line either.{\r}
