Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已经浪费够多时间…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I've spent a hell of a long time... What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这不是在帮忙 艾迪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're not helping... Eddie...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山姆 我们得讨论明天要拍的戏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sam, Sam. We gotta talk about those scenes tomorrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是一场灾难 是谁写的烂戏？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Disaster. Who the hell wrote that crap?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过 首先\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But, uh, first...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可以请你跳一支舞吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}May I have this dance?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾迪 你把我的酒弄洒了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Eddie... You're spilling my drink.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好玩吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Having fun?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}永远都这么好玩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Eternally.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}霍珀小姐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Miss Hopper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎收看《好莱坞日讯》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dateline, Hollywood.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}顶尖专栏作家赫达霍珀的办公室\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The offices of top columnist Hedda Hopper.{\r}
