Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里阳光普照 充满乐趣\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where all is sun and fun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗？众多名人聚集于此\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Or is it? You see the famous faces here?{\r}
