Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以及他美丽的新娘 洛琳·白考儿\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}his dishy bride Lauren Bacall.{\r}
