Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}联合罢工迅速转为暴力抗争\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in walkouts that quickly turned violent.{\r}
