Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是达尔顿·特朗勃\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And this is writer Dalton Trumbo,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和很多参加并支持罢工的人一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}who is, like many of those strikers and their supporters,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他也是共产党员\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a registered communist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}联合罢工的幕后黑手是谁？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Who exactly is behind these walkouts?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们创造了电影\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You actually create something...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样公平吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, is that fair?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不公平 不公平\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No! No!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的民选众议员\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our elected leaders will find out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}约翰·帕奈尔·汤马斯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Congressman J. Parnell Thomas{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}将率领非美活动调查委员会找出答案\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and his House Un-American Activities Committee.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}共产主义不是远在天边的威胁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Communism is not some faraway threat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最危险的共产分子就在美国\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's most dangerous agents are here,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}掌握了广播与银幕\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}controlling the airwaves and movie screens.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}控制了旗下的员工与工会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Taking over its employees and their unions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们必须认清 他们就是敌人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They need to be identified as the enemies they are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}共产分子的目标是统治世界\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}NARRATOR: Communists, their goal:\Nworld domination.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们发起新型战争\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The frontline of a new kind of war.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冷战\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A cold war.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}企图败坏民主价值\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A conspiracy to corrupt democratic values{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并推翻这个国家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and bring about the overthrow of this nation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅兹睡着了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mitzi fell asleep.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就是新闻里的那个人？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hey! That you in the news reel?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我没错\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes, it was.{\r}
