Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天啊 亲爱的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, my God! Honey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事 我没事 这伤不到我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, I'm all right, I'm all right. No harm done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are you sure? Oh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来吧 我们走\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Come on. Let's go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dad?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是共产党员吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are you a communist?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样犯法吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Is that against the law?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It is not.{\r}
