Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}激进分子？或许吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Radical? Maybe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有那些泼可乐的人才会觉得我危险\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dangerous. Only to men who fling Cokes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我热爱国家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I love our country.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们有一个好政府\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it's a good government.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但还可以好上加好 你不觉得吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But anything good could be better, don't you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈是共产党员吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Is Mom a communist?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Am I?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 我们来做个正规测验吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, why don't we give you the official test?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有一天 妈妈做了你最爱的午餐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mom makes your favorite lunch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火腿起司三明治\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ham and cheese.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火腿起司三明治\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ham and cheese.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到了学校 你发现有人没午餐吃\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And at school, you see someone with no lunch at all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你会怎么办？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What do you do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分享\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Share.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分享？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Share?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不会叫他们去找工作？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, you don't tell them to just go get a job?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不会给他们提供利率6%的贷款？这很明智的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh. You offer them a loan at 6%. Oh, that's very clever.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你是不把他们放在眼里？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ah, then you just ignore them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就是个小共产分子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You little commie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}特朗勃 你讲的话总是只有自己听得懂\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Trumbo, as usual, you only make sense to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是共产党员 我是民主党员\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, let them call you a communist, me a Democrat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这二个都是合法政党\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're both legitimate parties.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们虽然又贱又烂 但并不违法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yours is just meaner and duller, but there's nothing illegal about any of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 你等着瞧 - 汉特\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Yet... - Hunter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫你朋友别再偏执 好好喝酒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Tell your friend to dial down the paranoia and have a drink.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还觉得他不够偏执呢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I don't think he's being paranoid enough.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不会也这样吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Not you too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的冰块没了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're out of ice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我自作主张做了一本小册子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, I have taken the liberty of drawing up a pamphlet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主题是 国会还没注意到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The subject: Congress unaware of a little thing{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有个东西叫宪法第一修正案\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}called the First Amendment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们当然知道 只是不放在眼里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're aware of it. They just don't give a shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们只在乎这场美妙的新战争\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All they care about is this nice new war of theirs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们热爱战争 这场战争正合他们的意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These guys love war and this is a great one,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为既含糊不清 又恐怖而昂贵\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}'cause it's vague and it's scary and it's expensive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赞成的就是英雄 反对的就是叛徒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Anybody for it is a hero\Nand anybody against it is a traitor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正是如此 谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}IAN: Exactly, thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亚伦 别在画旁吸烟\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Arlen, not near the paintings.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别天真地以为他们拍完宣传影片就算了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And if you think this is about the movies, you're an idiot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我决定深入敌方阵营\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Which is why\NI'm going to have a little chat with the other side.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不会是指守护美国理想电影联盟吧？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You don't mean the Alliance, do you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你疯了吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are you out of your mind?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾迪 他们是演员 作家和导演\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Eddie, they're all actors and writers and directors,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像我们一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just like us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们是纳粹 只是太过小气不愿买制服\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're Nazis. They're just too cheap to buy the uniforms.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们把国会议员都请来了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They invited Congress out here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们不就是山姆·伍德和赫达·霍珀吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And are they all Sam Woods and Hedda Hoppers?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要妖魔化我们不了解的人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Please, let's not demonize people we don't really know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我赞成\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I say we go for it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道 他们请到谁来演讲吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And you know who you're gonna be talking to there, don't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}各位女士先生 欢迎约翰·韦恩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ladies and gentlemen, Mr. John Wayne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想谈谈一个我热爱的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I wanna say one thing about a place I love.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 不是好莱坞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, not Hollywood.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我喜欢好莱坞 但我更热爱美国\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I like Hollywood, but I love America.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}美国代表的就是自由\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}WAYNE: And when we talk about America,\NI'm talking about freedom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不惜加入世界大战也要捍卫到底\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The kind of freedom we just fought a world war to save.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想加入共产党？那就去吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You want to be a communist? Go be a communist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我在华府的朋友\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But some friends of mine in Washington{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}认为你们必须回答几个问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}think you got some questions to answer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我真不晓得 他这么会说话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I never knew he was this good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你们还想加入共产党…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}WAYNE: You still want to be a commie...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 因为他不是在表演 这才是他 - 去莫斯科吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- 'Cause he's not acting. That's him. - go be one in Russia.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去加入莫斯科大剧院芭蕾舞剧团吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But off you go and enjoy the Bolshoi Ballet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先生 想了解宪法第一修正案吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Excuse me, sir, would you like to read about the First Amendment?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 学习一点新知 - 你知道自己的权利吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Sir, a little education. - You know your rights?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}介绍宪法第一修正案的小册子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Pamphlet on the First Amendment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 只是份轻松读物 - 旅途愉快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- A little light reading. - Travels well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢你 山姆\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, thank you, Sam.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再见\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Do svidanya.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}印小册子是要钱的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It costs money to print those.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想了解宪法第一修正案吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How'd you like to learn\Nabout the First Amendment?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这简直是场恶梦\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is a nightmare.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}达顿\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dalton.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赫达 晚安\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, Hedda. Good evening to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亲爱的艾迪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Eddie, darling!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赫达\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hedda.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}新帽子？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}New hat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每天都要换一顶\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ah, daily, darling, daily.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你最近有去看电影吗 达顿？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Been to the movies lately, Dalton?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}杜克 你们说他是不是棒极了？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Duke. Now, wasn't he magnificent?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只是说出该说的话 你好 艾迪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just saying what needs saying. Hi, Eddie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好 杜克\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Duke.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听说你和朋友们印了本小册子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I hear you and your pals got a pamphlet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 有人拿吗？- 还没\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Any takers? - Not yet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想拿一本吗？我们是共产党员\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Uh, would you like one, sir? We're communists.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他是剧作家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He's a writer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里没有人会拿你们的册子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You won't get any takers. Not here, anyway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, why is that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上面只说国会没有权力调查\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All it says is that Congress has no right to investigate{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们给谁投票 去哪里祷告\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}how we vote or where we pray,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以及调查我们的思想言行和电影制作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}what we think, say or how we make movies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好 我叫达尔顿·特朗勃\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hello, I'm Dalton Trumbo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要国会认定是威胁 就有权力查到底\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Congress has the right to go after anything they think is a threat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们反对这样 重点是…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, that's where we disagree and that's the point.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们都应该有犯错的权利\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We both have the right to be wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想谈权利 先告诉我你站在哪一边\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You wanna talk about rights, first tell me whose side you're on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俄国已经没有朋友了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Russia's no friend, not anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们赶快清醒吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You'd better wake up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为新时代已经到来了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}'Cause it's a new day. A new day!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或许这时代不适合你这种人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And maybe it's not for your kind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我这种人？哪一种？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My kind? What kind is that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:13:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不明白我们如何打赢大战的人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The kind that has no idea why we just won a war.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真有趣 这是你第二次提及战事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's curious, that's the second time you mentioned that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以前在冲绳当战地记者\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}See, I was a war correspondent in Okinawa.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赫达的儿子被派驻在菲律宾\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hedda's son was stationed in the Philippines.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾迪在欧洲的战争情报局工作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Eddie was in Europe with the Office of War Information.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你当时在哪里服役呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Where did you serve again?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想说什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You trying to say something?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没什么 杜克\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, Duke, he wasn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你在二战中也有战功\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you're going to talk about World War II as if you personally won it,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就请说清楚你被派驻何处\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}let's be clear where you were stationed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在片场 化着妆 射空包弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On a film set, shooting blanks, wearing makeup.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你要揍我 我想先拿下眼镜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And if you're going to hit me, I would like to take off my glasses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}杜克 我们走\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Duke, come on. Let's get out of here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢你 达顿 我的下个专栏有东西写了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you, Dalton. My next column just wrote itself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幸好你不想妖魔化任何人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's a good thing you didn't want to demonize anybody{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}否则事情就尴尬了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or else that could have been awkward.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}曼尼不会说"多情"这个字\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Manny wouldn't say "amorous."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hang on one second.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保罗 请给我二包烟\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Paul, two packs, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 给你 - 谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Here you are. - Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}钱给你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Here you go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天啊 她真是无所不在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Good God, she's everywhere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这份合约将让你成为好莱坞薪酬最高的编剧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Your next deal's gonna make you the highest-paid writer in Hollywood.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是全世界收入最高的剧作家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Which will make you the highest-paid writer in the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是你应得的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You earned it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你深信自己写出的快乐结局\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You don't just write happy endings, you actually believe them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以观众才会买单\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's what people pay to see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}米高梅也才会雇用你 是吧 路易？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's why you belong here at MGM. Right, L.B.?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想让你们太容易得逞 那我在哪儿签名？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I hate to make the wooing too easy for you, but where do I sign?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有一个条件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just one thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如想替我工作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you're gonna work for me,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就不要再让我看到这种东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I never, ever want to see anything like this again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会的 我保证\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You won't. I promise.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要你不再读赫达霍珀的专栏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just stop reading Hedda Hopper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}路易跟你说了什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, what did L.B. say then?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别再提了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Jesus, don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直食不下咽 我的工作还不够辛苦吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I haven't eaten since. My job's not hard enough?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一点也不累\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Your job is not hard at all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你觉得在爆出新闻后 说服梅尔签下你很容易么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You think getting Mayer to sign you after those headlines was easy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公司提供破纪录的三年合约 供你在纸上胡说八道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You have a record-breaking three-year contract to make shit up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用谢我了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're welcome.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亲爱的 现在不是时候\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, honey, not now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜托 妈\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Please, Mom?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她真的可以\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}She really can.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 请她表演 - 可以怎样？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Ask her! - Can what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克莉欧 是真的吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Cleo, is this true?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们瞧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Watch this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 特朗勃… - 来啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Trumbo... - Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这是在向我挑战\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Of course, you realize this means war.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家注意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Behold!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有个非凡的母亲\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I had a very unusual mother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是 星妈\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Translation: stage mother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}杂技演员的悲惨童年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The misspent youth of a child acrobat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天啊 你参加了多久的演出？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My God, how long were you in show business?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直到我15岁 基本上算是强迫劳动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Till I was 15, but it was more show forced-labor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 厉害 - 真精彩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Bravo! - Brilliant!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}达尔顿·特朗勃先生？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mr. Dalton Trumbo?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们华盛顿见\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'll see you in Washington.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}祝你们野餐愉快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Enjoy your picnic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们走\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Let's go, boys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遵命 史崔普林先生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes, Mr. Stripling, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们发出了19张传票\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nineteen subpoenas have been issued to those we believe{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}传唤知悉好莱坞内共党阴谋的人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}have knowledge of the ongoing communist threat in Hollywood.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么阴谋？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What kind of threat is that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}企图败坏民主价值\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A conspiracy to corrupt democratic values{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并推翻这个国家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and bring about the overthrow of this nation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}利用电影？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Using movies?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道是哪部吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Any movie in particular or...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}电影是人类史上最具影响力的工具\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Movies are the most powerful influence ever created.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而隐身幕后的叛徒已染指电影\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And they are infested with hidden traitors.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}众议院非美活动调查委员会成立\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The House Un-American Activities Committee has been formed to investigate{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}调查好莱坞中可疑的共党分子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}alleged communists working in Hollywood.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}摄影机和一队记者记录了现场的情景\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The newsreel cameras and an army of newspapermen are on hand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}里根先生你是否知悉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mr. Reagan, has it been reported to you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有一小群人 或多或少\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There has been a small group more or less following the tactics{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和共产党有些接触\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that we, uh, associate with the Communist Party.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你认为他们是破坏分子吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And would you refer to them as a disrupting influence?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们有时试图成为破坏分子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I would say that, at times, they have attempted to be a disruptive influence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你认为电影界\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Do you believe that the motion picture industry{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已尽力不成为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is doing everything it can to rid itself{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}颠覆美国的势力吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of subversive un-American influences?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 共产党员无所不在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No. Communists are everywhere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们直接向莫斯科汇报\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They report directly to Moscow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煽动共产主义的人在许多场合\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On numerous occasions, communist agitators have tried hard{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}试图让我们沦陷于赤色思潮\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to steer us into the red river.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我们的立场坚定不移\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We had a little too much weight for that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你能指出几位煽动分子吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Will you name a few of these agitators?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:18:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欧文·皮切尔\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, Irving Pichel,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾迪华·狄米屈克 法兰克·杜托\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Edward Dmytryk, Frank Tuttle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若由我作主\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If I had my way about it,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就把他们全送回俄国\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they'd all be sent back to Russia{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或是其他不毛之地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or some other unpleasant place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们得在三天内出面作证\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We get our chance to testify in three days.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而这会损害我们的名誉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And what we're about to do won't make us too popular.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算我们被人诋毁 那又如何？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Okay, so we get slandered and then what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就用你的方式回答他们每一个问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You answer every question they ask in your own way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就别跟他们抬杠\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, don't tell them shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说得好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Beautifully put.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道他们给我们起的罪名吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, you know what they call that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们十之八九会被指为藐视国会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In all likelihood, we'll be cited for contempt of Congress.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们会被审判\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There will be a trial.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没听错吧？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What am I missing here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只听到了坐牢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All I'm hearing is jail.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不见得\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Not necessarily.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在低等法庭我们应该会输\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In a lower court, yes, we'll most likely lose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 但上诉之后 - 一定能成功\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- But on appeal... - It'll work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最高法院大法官九人中有五人是自由派\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Supreme Court is a five-to-four liberal majority.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们认为委员会违宪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They think this committee is unconstitutional.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不除不快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They want it killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听起来不错\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sounds great.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我退出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妮琪再见\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Niki.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们的计划我承担不起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Look, I can't afford this stuff you guys are talking about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}包括上诉最高法院以及法律费用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Supreme Court and legal fees...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}桃乐丝一定不会同意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You know, Dorothy's not gonna...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的情况已不乐观\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I mean, things already aren't great, but you know...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若再赌上所有积蓄 她会带孩子走人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If I dump all my savings into that, she's gone with the kids.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我帮你出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'll cover you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开销 旅费 诉讼费全由我付\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Expenses, travel, legal fees, everything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是你明明不喜欢我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You don't even like me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我喜欢你 是你不喜欢我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I like you fine. You don't like me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道吗 我不相信你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, you know what it is? I don't trust you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用我提 你也会继续说下去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, I'd say go on, but I'm afraid you will.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道自己有几两重\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Look, I know what I am. Okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我当然希望举国上下焕然新生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I want this whole country\Nto be different, top to bottom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若由我作主 没有人家里能有一座湖\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If I get what I want, nobody gets their own lake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的人生多无趣\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, that would be a very dull life, don't you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对你而言是如此\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah, for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但造湖工人不这么认为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Not for the guys who built this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或许是我错了 但从我们认识以来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If I'm wrong, tell me, but ever since I've known you,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你言论激进\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you talk like a radical.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}却仍过着富裕生活\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But you live like a rich guy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你没搞错\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That is true.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不觉得你会为了做正确的事牺牲这一切\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I don't think you're willing to lose all of this just to do the right thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我反对殉教 也不打没胜算的仗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, I despise martyrdom and I won't fight for a lost cause.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you're right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不愿失去一切 尤其是孩子们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm not willing to lose it all. Certainly not them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我愿意赌一把\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But I am willing to risk it all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是激进分子和有钱人的综合体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's where the radical and the rich guy make a perfect combination.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}激进分子依循耶稣的纯洁教诲奋战\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The radical may fight with the purity of Jesus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而有钱人则因撒旦的奸巧获胜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the rich guy wins with the cunning of Satan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}够了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎样？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜托你闭嘴 好吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just please shut up. Please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要我做什么都可以\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'll do whatever you want.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只求你别再跟我说这些鬼话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just please don't say shit like that anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我无法保证\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I can't guarantee that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:21:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}传唤的19人中 有10人抵达华盛顿\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In Washington, 10 of the original 19 subpoenaed{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开始在非美活动调查委员会面前作证\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}began their testimony before the House Un-American Activities Committee.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}特朗勃先生 请举起右手\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mr. Trumbo, raise your right hand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请宣誓 接下来所说的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Do you solemnly swear the testimony you are about to give{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}句句属实\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is the truth, the whole truth, nothing but the truth so help you God?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我发誓\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请坐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sit down, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}特朗勃先生 接下来我会问你一些问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mr. Trumbo, now I shall ask you a series of various questions{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你只需要回答是或不是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}all of which can be answered with a yes or a no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想回答是或不是 就会回答\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, I shall answer yes or no if I please to answer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会回答自己想说的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I shall answer in my own words.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是每个问题都能用或否来回答\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Many questions can be answered yes or no{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}除非对方是白痴或奴隶\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}only by a moron or a slave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}够了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's enough!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你拒绝回答问题吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are you refusing to answer the question?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主席 你的任何问题我都不会拒答\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mr. Chairman, I will refuse to answer none of your questions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你现在或曾经是否加入过共产党？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are you now or have you ever been\Na member of the Communist Party?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想提出证物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}May I introduce to evidence...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行 违反规则\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No. No! You are out of order!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 证据就是我写的剧本 - 不行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- my work, my screenplays... - No, no, no, no, no, no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你可能依此做出这样的判断\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by which you are making this determination?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一切由主席裁决\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, the chair will rule.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 但这是关键 - 不行 没有时间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- It's critical to... - No, just a minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的剧本太长了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Your screenplays are too long.{\r}
