Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.02,0:31:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 我不是故意的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"Yup, did it. Sorry, didn't mean it."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.82,0:31:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接着国会问你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So Congress then asks,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.73,0:31:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是否曾加入民主党？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"Are you now or have you ever been a Democrat?"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.07,0:31:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是民主党员 天啊 我觉得糟透了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I am and, God, I just feel awful about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.08,0:32:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后他们会要你供出民主党员名单\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Then they want the names of other Democrats.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.75,0:32:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}例如比尔 厄尔 奈特和汤姆\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Bill and Earl, Nate, Tom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.30,0:32:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会说 去吃屎吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Then I say, "Go to hell."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.67,0:32:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Really?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.43,0:32:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有哪些银行愿意资助政府的敌人？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How many banks fund enemies of the state?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.68,0:32:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}除非供出朋友的名字 否则拿不到钱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Your money's gone unless you give the names\Nof your friends here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.43,0:32:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们永远无法工作 但如此你才能存活\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They'll never work again,\Nbut it's the only way you ever will.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.65,0:32:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们彼此相熟 包括我们的家人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We all know each other, our families.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.82,0:32:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们是朋友\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're friends.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.16,0:32:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你会怎么做 巴迪？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What would you do, Buddy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.83,0:32:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Only you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.79,0:32:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会毁了别人一生最美好的一天\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Piss on the best day of a guy's life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.04,0:32:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Only you!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.68,0:32:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Christ's sakes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.72,0:33:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"根据协议…"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}According to the protocol set forth...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.73,0:33:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她会怎么说？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And what does she say?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.73,0:33:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公主会说什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What does the princess say?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.24,0:33:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可恶 烂透了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Shit... Shit!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.88,0:33:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"应该一点都不像才对"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Shouldn't be any likeness...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.38,0:33:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"这让我有点担心"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It concerns me a little bit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.42,0:33:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安 妮可拉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, good morning, Nikola.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.09,0:33:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以为你不能写剧本了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I thought you weren't allowed to write anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.26,0:33:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 只是剧本上不能有我的名字\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ah. No. No, just not allowed to put my name on it,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.94,0:33:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或直接付钱给我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or get paid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.77,0:33:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是什么状况？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How does that work?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.23,0:33:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}状况不太好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Not very well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.94,0:33:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这故事很有趣 轻松又浪漫\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's funny. It's breezy and romantic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.28,0:33:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是谁写的？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Who wrote it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.45,0:34:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你写的 老弟\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You did, old boy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.87,0:34:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的剧本写上你的名字\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You stick your name on my labor,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.96,0:34:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}交给公司就成了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}hand it in to your studio and we're in business.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.79,0:34:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没被传唤或列入黑名单只是侥幸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Look, it is just dumb luck that I wasn't subpoenaed and blacklisted myself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.09,0:34:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下一波审讯即将展开\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The hearings are going to start up again soon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.80,0:34:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也可能会被停工或解雇\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm going to get called and canned.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.92,0:34:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那手脚要更快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, then quick, lad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.30,0:34:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剧本卖成了 我们五五分帐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Let's sell this little beauty and split the take, 50-50.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.89,0:34:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}荒唐 我收一成就好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ridiculous. I'll take 10%.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.64,0:34:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你收二成 不 三成 这是我的底线\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You'll take 20. No, 30! And that's my final offer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.94,0:34:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是全世界最烂的生意人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're the worst businessman ever.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.82,0:34:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我讨厌这片名\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I hate the title.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.40,0:34:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Me too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.90,0:34:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪里不好？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Really? What's wrong with it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.15,0:34:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 《公主与乡巴佬》？ - 是啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- The Princess and the Peasant. - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.11,0:34:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜托 听起来像出偶剧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}God, please, Trumbo, it sounds like a puppet show.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.49,0:34:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就改掉吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, then, change it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.74,0:34:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}改了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.75,0:34:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的？你觉得这个名字更好？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Really? You think this title's better?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.08,0:34:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}《罗马假日》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Roman Holiday.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.46,0:34:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我喜欢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I like it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.30,0:34:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁让你加入的？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Who invited you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.67,0:34:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.51,0:34:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是我最喜欢的特朗勃家庭成员\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}She's my favorite Trumbo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.18,0:35:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要立法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm introducing legislation{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.11,0:35:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在此国家危急时刻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so in the event of a national emergency,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.10,0:35:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所有共产党员都会被送进俘虏收容所\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}all communists will be sent to internment camps.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.19,0:35:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总统支持此案么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the president supports this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.94,0:35:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他最好能支持\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.27,0:35:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}帕奈尔 我们得谈谈你的员工\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Parnell, I need to speak to you privately about your employees.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.99,0:35:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我先失陪了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Excuse me, gentlemen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.20,0:35:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些都是我家乡的合法支薪员工\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As I said, Bob, these are legitimate salaried employees from my home state.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.03,0:35:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但你没告诉我 他们都是你的亲戚\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What you didn't tell me is that every one of them is a relative.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.70,0:35:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这完全合法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Which is completely legal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.87,0:35:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是他们都没缴税\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Except that none of them pay taxes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.71,0:35:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等你的律师到场后再说吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Don't say anything else without a lawyer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.22,0:35:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.47,0:35:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}特朗勃太太 你好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mrs. Trumbo! Hi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.06,0:35:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}杰夫\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Jeff.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.97,0:35:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太太 你该付我工钱了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ma'am, I gotta get paid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.73,0:35:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh. I'm so sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.80,0:35:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的人都要养家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I got men with families.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.31,0:35:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我丈夫无法工作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My husband hasn't been able to get any work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.53,0:35:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们四处欠债\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We owe everyone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.24,0:35:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 太太 拜托 - 真的很抱歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Ma'am, please. - I'm so...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.24,0:36:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克莉欧 我们有钱了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Cleo, we're rich!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.74,0:36:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿去吧 杰夫\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There you are, Jeffrey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.12,0:36:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们的生活真刺激\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You people sure live exciting lives.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.75,0:36:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢你的帮忙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, I thank you. Appreciate it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.04,0:36:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也谢谢你贝蒂\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you, Betty!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.59,0:36:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们成功了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We did it, Cleo!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.38,0:36:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}派拉蒙买了《罗马假日》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We sold Roman Holiday! Paramount.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.22,0:36:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亲爱的 伊恩刚刚…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our beloved Ian is just...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.93,0:36:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Why, what's the matter?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.05,0:36:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拉特利奇大法官死了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Judge Rutledge died.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.34,0:36:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上个月死的是墨菲\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, no, that was Judge Murphy who died last month.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.43,0:36:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拉特利奇也死了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And Rutledge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.77,0:36:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昨晚过世\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Last night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.57,0:36:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别担心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, now...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.11,0:36:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一切都会没事的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Everything will be all right. You'll see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.41,0:36:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自由派大法官不占多数\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Without a liberal majority on the court,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.79,0:36:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上诉将被驳回\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}our appeal's gonna be denied.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.62,0:36:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是说 我们都要准备坐牢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Meaning we should all be prepared to go to prison.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.51,0:37:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算从头来过 我也不会改变任何决定\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I wouldn't change anything going back. Not one thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.69,0:37:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一年后我们再问问彼此吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Let's ask each other in a year.{\r}
