Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.96,0:45:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直是信奉自由主义的民主党员\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I have always been a Liberal Democrat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.09,0:45:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但多年来 在你家中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But in your home over the years,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.93,0:45:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}曾举行过多次政治集会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there have been political meetings attended by those{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.26,0:45:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}参与者都是共产党员\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that we now know to be communists.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.80,0:45:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的 我现在才搞清楚\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes, sir. Yes, that has now been made clear to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.18,0:45:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我家举行过无数活动与募款\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There were tremendous activities and fundraisers...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.60,0:45:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就在战时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that went on in my house during the war.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.32,0:45:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当时我不清楚\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I did not know then{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.82,0:45:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们隶属什么组织\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}all of their true affiliations{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.15,0:45:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}进行什么工作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or the work that they were up to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.87,0:45:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我从没想过他们可能是共产党员\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It never entered my mind\Nthat any of these people were communists.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.16,0:45:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们愚弄 利用 欺骗了我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I was duped and used. I was lied to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.13,0:45:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁利用你？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But who used you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.71,0:45:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呃…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, um...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.82,0:46:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或许就是这股邪恶势力策动所有组织\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These sinister forces who probably ran these organizations.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.55,0:46:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请说出你知道的人名\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, tell us the individuals that you have reference to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.19,0:46:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}罗宾森先生？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mr. Robinson?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.82,0:46:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有艾伯特·马尔兹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, uh, you had Albert Maltz.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.36,0:46:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法兰克·杜托 还有其他人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I knew Frank Tuttle and that other fellow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.87,0:46:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被他们称为政委的高层人士是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That top fellow who they say is the, uh, commissar out there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.37,0:46:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亚伦·赫德？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Arlen Hird?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.88,0:46:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错 亚伦·赫德\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes, yes, Arlen Hird.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.00,0:46:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不认识迪麦特雷克\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I didn't know Dmytryk at all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.75,0:46:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我现在成了政委\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm a commissar now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.55,0:46:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊恩·麦克连·汉特 以及…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ian McLellan Hunter... and{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.34,0:46:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}达尔顿·特朗勃\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dalton Trumbo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.06,0:46:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢你 罗宾森先生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you, Mr. Robinson.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.85,0:46:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢 先生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.23,0:47:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主席 我没有问题了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mr. Chairman, I have no further questions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.57,0:47:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这里 谁敢这样打小报告\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Snitch like that in here,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.53,0:47:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就死定了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you end up fucking dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.79,0:47:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾迪尽了责任 应当回到工作岗位\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Eddie ought to go back to work. He did what he had to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.21,0:47:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行 他是被逼才开口的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, no, he did what he was forced to do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.25,0:47:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}重点是他说了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, the point is, he did it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.76,0:47:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}勇敢的男人与男孩们 正与共产主义作战\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Brave men and boys are fighting this battle against communism.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.26,0:47:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们难以想像他们做了何等牺牲\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They are sacrificing in ways we can't even imagine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.93,0:47:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而你却担心这个混帐的电影事业？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And you wanna talk about some asshole's movie career?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.93,0:47:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我多希望艾迪及其党羽们的死\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'd see Eddie Robinson and everyone like him dead{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.65,0:47:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能换取朝鲜战场一个男孩的性命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}if it'd bring back one boy from Korea. Just one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.32,0:47:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾迪都合作了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So what are you saying?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.90,0:47:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道不能得到好处？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Guys like Eddie cooperate and get nothing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.78,0:47:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样不对\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That isn't right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.40,0:47:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说话小心点 杜克\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Careful, Duke.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.11,0:47:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么意思 赫达？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Or what, Hedda?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.41,0:47:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是我不小心会怎样？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If I'm not careful, what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.58,0:48:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不晓得原来你这么软趴趴\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I had no idea you were such a softie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.75,0:48:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 我就是柔软好抱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's me all right. All cuddles.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.26,0:48:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以你为荣\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Proud of ya, Eddie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.01,0:48:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这事不容易 但你做得很好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Wasn't easy, I know. But you did good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.60,0:48:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢 杜克\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thanks, Duke.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.31,0:48:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会致电片厂 片约将蜂拥而至\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm gonna call the studios. The offers will pour in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.36,0:48:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.66,0:48:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.33,0:48:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}美国史上和平时期最大的间谍案\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One of the greatest peacetime spy dramas{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.46,0:48:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已迈入高潮 罗森堡夫妇被判处死刑\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}reaches its climax,\Nas Julius and Ethel Rosenberg are sentenced to death{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.14,0:48:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为他们将核弹机密泄漏给苏俄\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for revealing atomic secrets to Soviet Russia.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.39,0:49:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}威斯康辛州的初级参议员 约瑟夫·麦卡锡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The junior senator from Wisconsin, Joseph McCarthy,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.02,0:49:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正加速调查可疑的共党分子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is ramping up his investigation into alleged communists he believes{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.19,0:49:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们可能已渗透入政府 军队和学校\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are infiltrating our government, our military, and our schools.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.36,0:49:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}敌人让叛徒和骗子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because the enemy has been able to get the traitors and dupes{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.40,0:49:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}潜入我们的政府进行工作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to do his work within our government.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.70,0:49:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在大学教职员中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One communist on the faculty{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.04,0:49:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个共产党员都不能留\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of one university is one communist too many.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.57,0:49:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人们必须忠诚 否则就是不忠诚\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A man is either loyal or he's disloyal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.17,0:49:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢你 比利\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you, Billy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.45,0:50:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们来了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're here! They're here!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.12,0:50:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们到家了 爸爸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're home! Dad!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.79,0:50:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}巨人进攻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm being attacked by giants! Ah!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.50,0:50:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的孩子怎么变得这么漂亮了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What have you beautiful creatures done with my little ones?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.46,0:50:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸 我们好想你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, Dad, we missed you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.59,0:50:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 克里斯多福 梅兹 - 你好 爸爸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Christopher. Mitzi. - Hi, Dad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.97,0:50:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My goodness.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.93,0:51:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妮可拉 瞧瞧你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nikola, look at you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.93,0:51:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她个子可真高\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}She got real tall.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.81,0:51:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是口红吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, is that lipstick?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.23,0:51:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dad...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.19,0:51:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好想念你们 你们每个人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, I've missed you so much. All of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.00,0:51:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是抱歉…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, I'm terribly sorry...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.50,0:51:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}巴迪 你好吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, Buddy! Well, how are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.46,0:51:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我对你无话可说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I got nothing to say to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.39,0:51:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}监狱似乎让我们染上了瘟疫\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Looks like prison has given us the plague.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.48,0:51:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 巴迪·罗斯一直都这么讨人厌\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah, well, that Buddy Ross, he was always an asshole.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.06,0:51:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.27,0:51:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他日子也不好过\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He's in trouble too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.90,0:51:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 三部电影都赔钱 - 真的吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Three movies, three flops. - Oh, really?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.53,0:51:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他想出卖灵魂 却不知灵魂在哪里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Look at him. He's trying to sell his soul, but he can't find it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.37,0:52:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希望他能撑到打完官司再破产\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I just hope he stays afloat long enough to get the shit sued out of him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.37,0:52:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗 谁告他？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, really? By whom?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.04,0:52:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你 我和大家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}By me and you and all of us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.28,0:52:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天哪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Jeez...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.97,0:52:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用他们的资本主义对付他们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We use their capitalist system against them...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.75,0:52:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上民事法庭索赔\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In civil court. We go after their money.{\r}
