Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.06,0:59:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些剧作家 他们都是…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And these writers, they're... They're all...{\r}
