Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.15,0:59:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜托 你也太胆小了吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Jesus, you're such a chicken-shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.99,0:59:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们正在和共产分子交战\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You know, we're at war with the communists.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.03,0:59:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 我们并没有 - 这是新型态的战争\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- No we're not. - It's a new kind of war.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.20,0:59:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错 根本不存在的战争 超新潮的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah, if it doesn't exist, very new.{\r}
