Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.67,0:59:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们只是没有躲过眼线\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They didn't steal it off a fucking camera truck.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.09,0:59:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们既然已经雇了打手\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So look, we bought a gorilla suit.{\r}
