Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.52,1:00:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就有时间再去找五份工作和五个写手\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, now I'm free to get five more jobs and five more writers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.36,1:00:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们每个人如法炮制\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And you each get five more jobs and five more writers and so on.{\r}
