Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.54,1:00:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁想写出轰动世界的电影？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So who wants to write a gorilla movie?{\r}
