Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.42,1:00:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在浓雾中与陌生人做生意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in thick fog among strangers.{\r}
