Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.06,1:00:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}千万别说 这里是特朗勃家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and when answering, never say, "Trumbo residence."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.06,1:00:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会用不同笔名和不同的制片人合作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'll be writing for various producers under different names.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.40,1:00:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不论谁来电 记得来找我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Whomever they ask for, you come find me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.90,1:01:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或留言\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Or take a message.{\r}
