Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.83,1:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不论何时都要有人应门\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The door must be answered at all hours.{\r}
