Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.44,1:01:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们要学习听写 速记和打字\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dictation, shorthand and typing will be learned.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.11,1:01:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成年人则负担最重要的工作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Those of legal age will have one of the most important jobs imaginable.{\r}
