Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.03,1:01:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有问题或担忧吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Any questions? Concerns?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.37,1:01:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 妮可拉 请说 - 有时间表吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Yes, Nikola. - Is there a schedule?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.46,1:01:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.62,1:01:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我得安排时间做作业\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I need to know when I can do homework.{\r}
