Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.21,1:02:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每周五 学生会还要开会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Plus, every other Friday, we have meetings for Student Council.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.63,1:02:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我必须…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm... I have to...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.05,1:02:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别担心 会有办法的 宝贝\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Niki, we'll figure something out, sweetheart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.80,1:02:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吧？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Won't we?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.85,1:02:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人们持续抗争 近期最高法院\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And protests continued as the Supreme Court may soon take up{\r}
