Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.97,1:02:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南方城镇的黑人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Negros in Southern towns and cities{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.08,1:02:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大量走上街头\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}have taken to the streets in large numbers.{\r}
