Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.57,1:02:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}许多未经证明的消息指出 可能发生暴动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There have been unconfirmed reports of disturbances and rioting.{\r}
