Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.62,1:03:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁是"葛拉汉·塔波"？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Which one is Graham Tauper?{\r}
