Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.39,1:03:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}《外星人与农庄女》是你写的？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you are The Alien and the Farm Girl.{\r}
