Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.13,1:04:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}该死的法兰克金\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, fuck Frank King.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.76,1:04:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我承诺要改写到他开心为止\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I said, until he's happy, I'd rewrite.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.59,1:04:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要为了这种垃圾开夜车？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you're gonna stay up with that all night, for that crap?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.35,1:04:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.43,1:04:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}达到他的文学与政治标准？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To get it to his high literary and political standards?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.10,1:04:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这东西不该扯上任何政治标准\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, it shouldn't be to anyone's political standards.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.94,1:04:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是《外星人与农庄女》 拜托\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's The Alien and the Farm Girl, for Christ's sake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.78,1:04:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你到底在想什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What the hell were you thinking?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.19,1:04:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在想\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I was thinking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.61,1:04:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是我写作的初衷 写出重要的事物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's why I'm a writer. To say things that matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.11,1:04:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还记得吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Remember that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.53,1:04:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是曾入围普利兹奖的记者\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I was a reporter. I was nominated for a Pulitzer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.79,1:04:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在西班牙服役 还认识海明威\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I fought in Spain, and I know Ernest Hemingway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.21,1:04:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 我真的认识他 - 胡说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I actually... I know him. - Oh, bullshit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.04,1:04:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他也认识我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And he knows me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.29,1:04:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}假如在巴黎的酒吧遇见他\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If I walked into a bar in Paris, he...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.80,1:04:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他可能不记得我名字\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Maybe not my name, but he'll...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.22,1:04:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但至少会招手\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'll get a wave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.34,1:04:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希望如此\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.80,1:04:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你得过该死的国家图书奖\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You... You won the National fucking Book Award.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.39,1:04:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但现在我们在做什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I mean, what are we doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.52,1:05:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回到正题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Okay, so the alien...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.48,1:05:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外星人让农庄女怀孕了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The alien impregnates the farm girl.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.65,1:05:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 没错 - 为什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Right. - Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.82,1:05:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为他想播种并繁殖新的物种\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Because he wants to inseminate her and propagate a new species{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.36,1:05:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 然后占领地球？ - 不\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- on Earth and take over? - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.65,1:05:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为她让他想起家乡的女孩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Because she reminds him of the girl he left behind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.74,1:05:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但他头这么大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But he's got a bug head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.87,1:05:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他家乡的女孩 头一定也很大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}His girlfriend's probably got a bug head back home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.08,1:05:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人不会迷恋外表\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You don't get hung up on the looks of someone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.37,1:05:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他爱上了她\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He's falling in love with her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.83,1:05:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Uh, okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.33,1:05:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想太多了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're over-thinking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.26,1:05:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 你还好吗？ - 还好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Are you all right? - Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.18,1:05:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不要休息一下？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You want to do this later?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.01,1:05:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 请继续\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No. Go, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.85,1:05:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.35,1:05:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道你不怀念过去的时光？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I mean, do you ever miss writing something...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.52,1:05:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不说是伟大 但至少是好作品\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Forget great, just good?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.19,1:05:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你脑中一定有很多好点子 是吧？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I mean, you must have ideas still, right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.90,1:05:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有几个\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I've got a few.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.78,1:05:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其中有一个萦绕不去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's one that won't go away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.78,1:06:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好几年前 克莉欧和我在墨西哥看斗牛\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Cleo and I are in Mexico at a bullfight years ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.58,1:06:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那只牛死了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the bull dies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.75,1:06:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成千上万的观众却在欢呼\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And, uh, thousands of people are just cheering.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.09,1:06:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}除了三个人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Three weren't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.05,1:06:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克莉欧 我 我们前面的一个小男孩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Cleo, me and this young boy down front,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.93,1:06:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他哭了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}crying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.98,1:06:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直好奇他哭的原因\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Always wondered why.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.11,1:06:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等你找到答案后 就会写出来了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, (COUGHS) you write it and you'll know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.61,1:06:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}答应我 别交给该死的法兰克金\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But please promise me, not for Frank fucking King.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.66,1:06:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜托\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.58,1:06:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}颁发最佳编剧奖的演员也热爱阅读\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To present the writing awards, here is an actor who also reads.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.37,1:06:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎柯克·道格拉斯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mr. Kirk Douglas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.87,1:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妮琪 快点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Niki, hurry!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.92,1:06:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是谁颁奖？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Who's doing it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.55,1:06:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来了来了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm coming, I'm coming!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.89,1:07:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}信封\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The envelope.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.43,1:07:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥斯卡得主是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the Oscar goes to{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.73,1:07:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}《罗马假日》编剧 伊恩·麦克连·汉特\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Roman Holiday by Ian McLellan Hunter. (GASPS){\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.65,1:07:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}万岁 爸 你得奖了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes! That's you, Dad, that's you!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.98,1:07:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸 太棒了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dad, that is fantastic!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.53,1:07:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我代表伊恩·麦克连·汉特领奖\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is accepted on behalf of Ian McLellan Hunter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.70,1:07:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们可以过幸福快乐的生活了吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So do we get to be happy now?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.30,1:07:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想要\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I don't want it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.97,1:07:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不想要\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, I don't want it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.01,1:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上面写了你的名字\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Your name's on it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.64,1:07:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但剧本是你写的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You wrote it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.18,1:07:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们把奖给了你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They gave it to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.81,1:07:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它让我创造了奇迹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it's done me wonders.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.61,1:07:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是轰动世界的剧本\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Here's the gorilla script.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.24,1:07:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 爸 - 在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Hey, Dad. - Ah?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.61,1:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有你的电话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Phone for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.32,1:08:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找哪个名字？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For which name?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.03,1:08:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找你 一个叫巴迪·罗斯的人打来的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, you. Some guy named Buddy Ross.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.20,1:08:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看来传言是真的？《罗马假日》是你写的？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, is the rumor true? You wrote Roman Holiday?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.92,1:08:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能帮上什么忙吗 巴迪？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What can I do for you, Buddy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.59,1:08:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}电影票房失利 让我坠入万丈深渊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My movies have all bombed. Dug me into a hole.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.93,1:08:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}终于要拍一部\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I finally got something going.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.85,1:08:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}超级大片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Classy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.05,1:08:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我找来三位巨星 但剧本…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Three big stars. The script...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.23,1:08:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别提了 根本没剧本\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What script? There is no script.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.19,1:08:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我找了11个作家都写不好 演员即将退出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I got 11 writers who fucked me and now the actors are gonna pull out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.73,1:08:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若真如此 我将失去一切\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And if they do, I lose everything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.32,1:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你何时要拍？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When do you shoot?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.78,1:08:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}十天后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ten days.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.37,1:08:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有任何参考资料吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Is there anything?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.12,1:08:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当然 我无法让你署名\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There'd be no credit, obviously.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.00,1:08:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开拍后才能支付酬劳\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I can't pay you till we start shooting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.63,1:09:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是你唾弃我 我不会怪你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I wouldn't blame you if you spit in my face.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.60,1:09:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我们曾经合作过好作品\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But we did good stuff back then.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.43,1:09:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We really did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.77,1:09:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜托你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.90,1:09:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还要帮金氏兄弟改写一部剧本\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I owe the King Brothers a rewrite.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.24,1:09:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无法两者兼顾\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And I can't do both.{\r}
