Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.68,1:15:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有时确实难以忍受 尤其是最近\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, it's challenging sometimes, especially lately.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.01,1:15:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不如跟我一起去躺楼下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hey, why don't you come downstairs with me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.02,1:15:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想给你看一样东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I wanna show you something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.82,1:15:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有看见我的手套吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You see my gloves?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.94,1:15:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.62,1:15:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你拿这当他的头来打吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Do you imagine that's his head?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.25,1:15:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 但你可以\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No. But you can.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.23,1:16:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妮可 剧本好了吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Niki, is that the script already?{\r}
