Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.94,1:16:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟你爸说…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ah. Tell your dad that...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.18,1:16:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好 我找亚伦·赫德\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, hello. Um, I'm looking for Arlen Hird.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.14,1:16:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}特朗勃先生 我是安德鲁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mr. Trumbo, it's Andrew.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.93,1:16:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天啊 你长这么大了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Good God! Look... Look at you!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.31,1:16:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想你爸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Wow. Well, I'm certain your father{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.28,1:16:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定说过我的坏话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}has told you some nasty things about me,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.61,1:17:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟你保证\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but I want to assure you,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.11,1:17:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他说的都是真的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they're all true.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.91,1:17:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他在家吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Is, uh... Is he home?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.04,1:17:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 我以为你有听到消息\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm sorry. I thought you knew.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.56,1:17:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 真遗憾 - 非常感谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I'm so sorry. - Thank you so much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.10,1:17:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安德鲁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Andrew.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.48,1:17:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}约书亚\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Joshua.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.44,1:17:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸留了一样东西给你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My dad left something for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.53,1:17:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是份记录\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's a record.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.49,1:17:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}记了他欠你和其他人的钱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Money that he owed you and some other people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.91,1:17:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 我也希望能把钱还清\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm sorry. I wish we could pay you back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.12,1:17:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别这么说 安德鲁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Andrew, no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.04,1:17:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我欠他的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I owed him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.34,1:18:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些都是我欠的债\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The debts are all mine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.93,1:18:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.08,1:18:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好 艾迪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hello, Eddie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.79,1:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没想到你会来找我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is a bit of a surprise.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.96,1:18:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什么事吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What can I do for you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.05,1:18:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亚伦死了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Arlen died.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.64,1:18:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在外景拍戏时听说了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I heard. I was on location.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.98,1:18:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是你当初捐给辩护基金的钱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is the money you gave us for the defense fund.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.44,1:18:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们欠你的 包括亚伦在内\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's everything that we owe you. Arlen included.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.77,1:19:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 我不打算要回来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, now, that was a gift.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.23,1:19:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我们希望把账结清\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We'd like it off our books.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.03,1:19:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么意思？你话中有话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What is this supposed to be? Some kind of message?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.62,1:19:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你 亚伦和好莱坞十君子都瞧不起我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What you and Arlen and the great Hollywood Ten all think of me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.54,1:19:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好吧 但请听我解释\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Fine. Fine. But first you're gonna listen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.55,1:19:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在你坐牢之后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}After you went to jail,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.01,1:19:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一整年都没有工作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I didn't work for a year.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.60,1:19:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有戏约 连试演都没有\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No offers, not even an audition.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.90,1:19:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人人都与我保持距离\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}People would see me, cross the street.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.28,1:19:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些我爱的人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}People I loved.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.57,1:19:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以及靠我发大财的人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}People I made rich.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.28,1:19:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我被传唤至委员会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I sat in front of that committee.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.74,1:19:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是为什么 我可什么也没做\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Why? I didn't do anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.41,1:19:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们什么都没做 只是不懂事的小娃儿\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}None of us did anything. We were all stupid babies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.62,1:20:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没做任何不法勾当\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}With no business in any of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.79,1:20:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只想回到原本的生活\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I just wanted my life back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.30,1:20:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们掌握了每一个名字 包括你和亚伦\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They had every name. Yours, Arlen's, everybody's.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.14,1:20:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我提供的资讯 他们早就有了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I didn't give them anything they didn't already have.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.47,1:20:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我终结了这一切 仅此而已\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I ended it, is all. I just... I ended it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.44,1:20:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾迪 提供他们无权过问的资讯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, Eddie, you don't end something like this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.28,1:20:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没办法终结任何事情\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}By giving them what they have no right to ask.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.32,1:20:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要教我该怎么做吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're gonna tell me how I should have handled it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.58,1:20:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像你对付议会那样？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Like you handled Congress?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.08,1:20:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道你以这件事情为荣吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you're saying that you're proud of what you did?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.12,1:20:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁有资格感到荣耀？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Proud? Who the hell gets to be proud?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.00,1:20:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You. You do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.50,1:20:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}使用那些假名和掩护\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You with your fake names and your fronts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.63,1:20:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成功重返编剧事业\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You've got all the work you want.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.09,1:20:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而我却必须每天亲身面对世界\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I gotta go out in the world every day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.18,1:20:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是我的工作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is my work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.06,1:20:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没办法化身为另一个人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I've got nobody else to be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.85,1:21:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我当时别无选择\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I did what I had to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.02,1:21:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你做得心甘情愿 艾迪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You did what you wanted, Eddie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.52,1:21:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了获得更大的成功\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And you did it for more.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.94,1:21:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接拍更多电影 赚更多钱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}More movies, more money,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.66,1:21:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}买更多死人画的烂东西挂在墙上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}more dead bullshit on your walls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.46,1:21:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的事我自己承担 但你害亚伦\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What I did, I did, but did you ever wonder how many years{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.25,1:21:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少活了多少年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you hacked off Arlen's life?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.05,1:21:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只为了昭告天下 自己是个叛逆天才？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To show the world what a rebel genius you are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.31,1:21:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你必须承担这个责任\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You live with that!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.91,1:21:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个人喝吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Drinking alone?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.16,1:21:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我愿意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Preferably.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.54,1:22:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你最近都在忙什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And what are you up to these days?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.29,1:22:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赫达 也许再喝一杯我就会告诉你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You know, Hedda, another one of these and I just may tell you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.21,1:22:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我请你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, then I'm buying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.59,1:22:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一样的再来一杯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Usual. Same again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.01,1:22:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 霍珀小姐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes, Miss Hopper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.72,1:22:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜托 我听见谣言了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, come on, I hear the rumors.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.06,1:22:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}告诉我 你仍在战场上英勇奋战\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Show me you're still in the game, fighting the good fight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.64,1:22:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快来打我的脸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Come on, rub my face in it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.60,1:22:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}告诉我你在偷偷写哪一部片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Whisper a movie you've written in secret.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.98,1:22:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或许我已经听说过了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Maybe I've even heard of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.78,1:22:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或许吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Maybe you have.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.19,1:22:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 拍片忙坏我了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sorry, sorry, sorry, sorry... I'm filming. It's crazy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.20,1:22:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}巴迪 你认识达尔顿·特朗勃吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Buddy, do you know Dalton Trumbo?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.00,1:22:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}认识 我们以前曾经合作过\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes, I believe we have worked together before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.67,1:22:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是在米高梅吗？好几百年前的事了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What was it? Was it MGM?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.25,1:22:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很高兴再次见到你 巴迪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A million years ago. Nice to see you again, Buddy.{\r}
