Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.02,1:33:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}《勇敢的人》是不是你的作品？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Did you write The Brave One?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.37,1:33:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一向不作声称\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, you see, it's my policy{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.13,1:33:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自己参与过任何电影\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}not to claim credit for any one movie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.34,1:34:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不然每部电影岂不是都有我的份\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That way, it's possible that I had something to do with all of them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.97,1:34:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当然烂片除外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Except the stinkers, which were all written{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.05,1:34:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那都是我的敌人们写的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by my enemies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.72,1:34:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在黑名单属于哪个位置？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What's your position on the blacklist?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.39,1:34:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就在黑名单上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, on it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.39,1:34:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟另外数千人列在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Along with thousands of others.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.64,1:34:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是否试图以劳勃·瑞奇的争议终结黑名单？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are you using this Robert Rich controversy to try and end it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.40,1:34:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}《勇敢的人》是部好片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}See, The Brave One is a nice little picture.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.57,1:34:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果谣传我有参与该片能帮助票房\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And if rumors of my involvement{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.41,1:34:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我欣然接受\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}can help sell tickets, well, then, good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.66,1:34:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果这种作者不明的怪事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And if the strange circumstances{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.25,1:34:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能激起讨论\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of its authorship raised a few questions,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.04,1:34:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就更好了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}well, even better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.54,1:34:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 特朗勃 - 是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Trumbo? - Yes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.21,1:34:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 有人来电找你 - 是谁？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Phone for you. - Well, who is it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.76,1:34:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自称寇克·道格拉斯的疯子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Some crazy guy, says he's Kirk Douglas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.22,1:34:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的？谢谢你 妮可拉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Really? Huh. Well, thank you, Nikola.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.07,1:35:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是妮可？我是寇克\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Niki? Kirk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.91,1:35:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寇克\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Kirk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.45,1:35:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}达顿\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dalton.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.91,1:35:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My apologies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.04,1:35:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最近有太多恶作剧电话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We've had more than our share of crank calls lately.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.79,1:35:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 我能想像 - 请坐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I can imagine. - Please have a seat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.59,1:35:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想喝什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}May I get you a drink?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.75,1:35:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不必了 谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No. No thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.88,1:35:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.47,1:35:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 所以？- 我接了一支新片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- So? - I'm doing a new picture.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.93,1:35:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚刚收到剧本\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And I just got the script.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.72,1:35:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看来是长达七小时的娱乐大片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That must be seven hours of entertainment there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.23,1:35:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是没有一页有趣\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Not a single page is entertaining.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.81,1:35:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但里头有个动人故事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But there's a good story in there somewhere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.15,1:35:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}关于一个试图对抗全世界的男人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}About one man who tried to take on the whole world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.32,1:35:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这有点意思\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, you've got me so far.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.95,1:35:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身为奴隶的他 起义反抗罗马帝国\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He was a slave who led a revolt against the Roman Empire.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.16,1:35:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}片名叫什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, what's the title?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.08,1:35:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}《斯巴达克斯》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Spartacus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.00,1:36:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不不不\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, no, no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.13,1:36:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不能说自己正在写什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I can't tell you what I'm working on now, except to say that{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.09,1:36:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能说 既然有黑名单 就有黑市\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the blacklist is alive and well and so is the black market.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.76,1:36:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的 你可以引用这段话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, yes, you can quote me on that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.47,1:36:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看见我的名字上报 会让一些人抓狂\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Seeing my name in the papers drives certain people out of their minds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.10,1:36:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他来了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Of course. Here he is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.81,1:36:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 你好 寇克 - 你好 赫达\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Kirk. - Hedda.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.19,1:36:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他是我朋友 鲍伯·史崔普林\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'd like you to meet a friend of mine, Bob Stripling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.69,1:36:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来自非美活动调查委员会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}House Un-American Activities Committee.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.53,1:36:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}道格拉斯先生 你好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mr. Douglas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.03,1:36:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}史崔普林先生 你好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mr. Stripling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.37,1:36:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喝点东西吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Drink?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.66,1:36:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不了 谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.00,1:36:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有要事找我？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You said it was important.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.50,1:36:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要你雇用了达尔顿·特朗勃\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Only if you hired Dalton Trumbo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.22,1:36:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我雇谁是我的事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Who I hire is my business.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.72,1:36:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 道格拉斯先生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, Mr. Douglas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.22,1:36:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这关我们的事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's ours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.05,1:36:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.18,1:36:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我们要维护美国的安全\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}'Cause we have to keep this country safe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.39,1:36:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么维护？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And how are you doing that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.14,1:37:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不请你上证人席看看吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, why don't I show you by putting you on the stand?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.15,1:37:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赫达 你朋友打算恐吓我？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hedda, is your friend trying to scare me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.73,1:37:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他只是想让你知道 该怎么做事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He's just trying to show you the way things are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.99,1:37:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或许我不喜欢这样做事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Maybe I don't like the way things are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.32,1:37:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寇克 我们认识多年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Kirk, we've known each other a long time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.91,1:37:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你什么时候变成了一个混帐？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Since when did you become such a bastard?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.58,1:37:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直都是个混帐 只是你没发现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I was always a bastard. You just never noticed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.77,1:37:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么事？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.86,1:37:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想见这部戏的编剧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I wish to see the man who wrote this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.19,1:37:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请进\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Please, come in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.91,1:37:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.95,1:38:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是奥图·普莱明杰\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I am Otto Preminger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.29,1:38:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是个导演\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The director.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.92,1:38:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Forgive me, I...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.09,1:38:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我几个小时前才刚忙完\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I've just finished work a few hours ago. I...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.80,1:38:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我读完了你的剧本\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A copy of which I've read.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.72,1:38:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么可能？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But how could...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.30,1:38:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我今天早上才寄出的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I just had that delivered this morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.26,1:38:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是奥图·普莱明杰 我是导演\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I am Otto Preminger, the director.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.93,1:38:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请进\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.40,1:38:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我最小的孩子认为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, yes, my youngest thinks{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.65,1:38:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}养鸟可以纾压\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that I can end the suffering of all broken birds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.83,1:38:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我都是吃烤鸟纾压\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As can I, with a broiler.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.75,1:38:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寇克·道格拉斯委托你的剧本 写完了吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are your duties completed for Mr. Kirk Douglas?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.17,1:38:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 但我有两周的圣诞假期\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, but I do have two weeks off for Christmas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.67,1:38:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这段期间你要跟我一起工作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}During which time you will work with me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.30,1:38:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Will I?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.18,1:39:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你跟你的剧本一样聪明\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you're as intelligent as your writing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.18,1:39:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并且与你的名声一样贪婪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And as greedy as your reputation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.02,1:39:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们要改编小说《出埃及记》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It is an adaptation of the novel Exodus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.36,1:39:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你读过吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You've read it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.52,1:39:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.03,1:39:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是本超级畅销书\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A colossal bestseller.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.28,1:39:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}几乎难看得要死\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Very nearly a perfect piece of shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.11,1:39:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但里头有个好故事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But there's a good story in there somewhere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.04,1:39:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没概念\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I have no idea.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.00,1:39:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我找来了保罗·纽曼\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But I have Paul Newman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.33,1:39:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们谈过了 他有点谨慎\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We have spoken. He is a little reticent,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.21,1:39:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但价钱谈拢 他就会接受\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but I believe, at the right price, he will accept.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.30,1:39:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要接吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you're doing it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.84,1:39:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是唯一能赶走他的方法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, I think it's the only way to get him to leave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.51,1:39:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这很要紧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's very important.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.22,1:39:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可怜的普莱明杰先生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Poor Mr. Preminger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.98,1:39:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他以为他是猫 而你才是老鼠\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He thinks he's the cat and you're the mouse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.91,1:40:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瞧瞧 太棒了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, look at that. Perfect.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.02,1:40:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅兹那是什么？俄罗斯娃娃？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hey, Mitzi, what's that? A Russian doll?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.67,1:40:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是什么 圣诞老人？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh! What is this, Santa?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.83,1:40:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}献给圣诞婆婆的小心意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just a little something for Mrs. Claus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.88,1:40:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我等等再拆\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'll open it later.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.17,1:40:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}圣诞节结束了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Christmas is over.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.01,1:40:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.72,1:40:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你读了最新写的那几场戏？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Did you read the new scenes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.35,1:40:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}糟透了 继续保持这种水准\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dreadful. Keep up this level of work,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.60,1:40:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的名字就会在我的电影里出现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and I will see to it your name is on my movie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.44,1:40:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以承受骂名\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To take the blame.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.07,1:40:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 拿去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, there you go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.71,1:40:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好 山米\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ooh! Hello. Hi, Sammy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.29,1:40:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道它是寇克·道格拉斯送的吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, do you know that Kirk Douglas gave me this bird?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.13,1:40:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它会害你分心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's a distraction.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.26,1:40:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完全不会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No. No, not at all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.30,1:41:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我给它取名为山姆·杰克森\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I named him Sam Jackson.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.64,1:41:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}《斯巴达克斯》就是他写的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He wrote Spartacus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.06,1:41:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如何？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.14,1:41:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 有进步 - 感谢老天\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Better. - Thank God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.90,1:41:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但还不是天才之作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But it simply lacks genius.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.48,1:41:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥图 如果每场戏都很精彩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Otto, if every scene is brilliant,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.65,1:41:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的电影会变得单调乏味\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}your movie is going to be utterly monotonous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.32,1:41:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我告诉你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'll tell you what.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.62,1:41:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你把每一场戏写得精彩无比\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You write every scene brilliantly,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.75,1:41:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而我会导得高潮迭起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and I will direct unevenly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.50,1:41:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么事 亲爱的？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What is it, dear?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.34,1:41:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.84,1:41:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哈啰 寇克\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, hello, Kirk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.18,1:41:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}圣诞快乐 谢谢你 梅兹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Merry Christmas. Thank you, Mitzi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.35,1:41:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥图 你好吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Otto. How are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.14,1:41:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我很好 寇克\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I am very well, Kirk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.14,1:41:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我无意打断你们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I, uh, didn't mean to interrupt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.36,1:41:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 没这回事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, no. No, not at all. Not at all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.53,1:42:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥图 请让我们谈谈\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Otto, would you mind if we had a little chat?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.99,1:42:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一会儿就好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Won't be a second.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.53,1:42:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还以为撞见了自己的老婆\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I sort of feel like I walked in on my wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.70,1:42:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你喜欢他吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Do you love him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.87,1:42:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可怕极了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, it's far more lurid than that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.04,1:42:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他竟然付费买我的服务\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He's paying me for my services.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.00,1:42:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So am I.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.13,1:42:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}按约定 我会在1月2日向你交稿\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And you'll get them again, January 2nd, as promised.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.63,1:42:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只需要你拨冗几天 写几场新戏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I just need you a few days on some of the new scenes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.47,1:42:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当然 但要等2号以后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Of course, but not until the 2nd.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.22,1:42:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不想这样 但我没遇过\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I wouldn't ask, but I've never had a director{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.23,1:42:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比库伯·力克更令人头痛的导演\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}who's a bigger pain in my ass than Stanley Kubrick.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.23,1:42:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最糟的是 他是对的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The worst part is, he's right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.73,1:42:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想拒绝你 但…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, I wouldn't refuse, but...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.41,1:42:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是我们之间的秘密\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, I really... This should remain between us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.70,1:42:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当然\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.58,1:42:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}普莱明杰宣称\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Preminger has declared that...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.58,1:42:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, what he said was,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.71,1:43:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"继续保持这种水准"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"You keep up this level of work,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.26,1:43:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"你的名字就会在我的电影里出现"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"and I'll see to it that your name is on my movie."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.76,1:43:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 真的吗？ - 没错\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Really? - Oh, yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.76,1:43:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一字不假\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Those were his exact words.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.77,1:43:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保持联系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Be in touch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.35,1:43:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Very well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.86,1:43:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}圣诞快乐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Merry Christmas!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.19,1:43:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.28,1:43:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我猜他想要你回去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I suppose he wants you back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.03,1:43:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, no. No, no. He...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.70,1:43:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他来串门 顺便讨论演职人员名单\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He just stopped by to talk about a screen credit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.17,1:43:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}《斯巴达克斯》的名单？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On Spartacus?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.34,1:43:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不能透露任何细节\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, I really shouldn't have said anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.30,1:43:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你懂的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You understand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.34,1:43:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}休息五分钟 大家五分钟后回来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Five minutes! Back in five minutes, everybody!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.43,1:43:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寇克\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Kirk,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.60,1:43:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赫达·霍珀说 如果你不解雇特朗勃\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hedda Hopper just told me the American Legion is going to boycott us{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.48,1:44:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}退伍军人协会将发动抵制活动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}unless you get rid of Trumbo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.61,1:44:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾德 本片剧本与他无关\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ed, he's not done with the script.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.98,1:44:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}片中没有他的名字\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}His name will never be on the thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.44,1:44:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什么好抵制的？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What's anybody boycotting?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.99,1:44:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寇克 不好意思\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Kirk... Just a second. Please. Please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.57,1:44:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请让我们独处一会儿\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just give me five seconds, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.16,1:44:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}二千万美国人明确表示\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Listen. Twenty million Americans are saying loud and clear,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.16,1:44:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不解雇一位编剧 他们就不买票\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they will never buy a ticket to our movie unless you fire one writer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.08,1:44:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里有50人 选一个吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Here's 50! Pick one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.36,1:44:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可以插句话吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mind if I stick my nose in?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.15,1:44:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.36,1:44:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他知道内幕 他看见寇克·道格拉斯进出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He knows. He sees Kirk Douglas coming in and out of here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.07,1:44:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以及奥图·普莱明杰和他的劳斯莱斯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And Otto Preminger and his Rolls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.45,1:44:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他是个白痴 但他并不笨\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He's an idiot. But he's not stupid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.04,1:45:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他向联邦调查局告密了吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Has he called the FBI?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.25,1:45:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}国会呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Congress?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.63,1:45:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有 因为他们能给你的惩罚早就给了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, because everything they can do, they've already done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.17,1:45:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那座奥斯卡奖是属于你的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That Oscar belongs to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.30,1:45:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去拿回来吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Get it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.56,1:45:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天啊 你一点都不像我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My God! You're nothing like me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.98,1:45:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你比我更可怕\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're worse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.11,1:45:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请你正式声明 你是劳勃·瑞奇？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For the record, you're Robert Rich?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.78,1:45:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.86,1:45:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我看过名单了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I've been through the whole list, Ed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.41,1:45:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上面都是假名\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're all hacks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.70,1:45:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}《勇敢的人》是你写的？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And you wrote The Brave One?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.70,1:45:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.04,1:45:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾德 我等等回电给你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ed, let me call you back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.12,1:45:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为何你现在站出来？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Why come forward now?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.75,1:45:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我被非美活动调查委员会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, as someone who has been thoroughly investigated{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.55,1:45:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彻底调查过\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by the House Un-American Activities Committee,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.80,1:45:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我实在好奇 为何没人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I started wondering, why hasn't anyone taken{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.14,1:45:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}审查这个组织\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a good long look at them{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.18,1:45:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以及他们对电影产业造成的影响？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and their work in the movie industry?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.68,1:46:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}该组织的宗旨是 揪出敌方特工\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You see, they were convened to uncover enemy agents,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.15,1:46:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}揭露共产阴谋 并制定反叛乱法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}expose communist conspiracies and write anti-sedition laws.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.78,1:46:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但经过了数千小时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, here we are, thousands of hours{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.99,1:46:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}耗费了数百万元之后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and millions of dollars later.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.82,1:46:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有任何特工被揪出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Agents uncovered, zero.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.37,1:46:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有任何阴谋被揭露 没有任何法条被制定\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Conspiracies exposed, zero. Laws written, zero.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.58,1:46:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们所做的只是否定别人的工作权\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You see, all they do is deny people their right to work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.21,1:46:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我因此丧失权益\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And they can't even get that right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.59,1:46:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以及二座奥斯卡奖\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Academy Awards, two.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.14,1:46:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你作何感想？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And how does that feel?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.52,1:46:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}深深伤害你的黑名单 竟然只是个笑话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To have so undermined the blacklist that it's almost a joke.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.60,1:46:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笑话？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A joke?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.11,1:46:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这张创造出劳勃·瑞奇的黑名单\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I know the blacklist that produced Robert Rich.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.70,1:46:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我见过它的可怕与残酷\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I've seen its horror and cruelty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.87,1:47:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它可憎地浪费我过去的人生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A hideous waste of life{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.08,1:47:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只能长年做个无名氏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as I've walked in the long line of its anonymous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.75,1:47:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我无法再巧妙捏造出下个劳勃·瑞奇\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And I cannot invent one more witticism about Robert Rich{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.38,1:47:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或另一座无人能认领的奥斯卡奖\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or the Oscar he can't claim.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.64,1:47:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为那座小小的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Because that small,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.98,1:47:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毫无用处的小金人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}worthless golden statue{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.94,1:47:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上面沾满了我朋友们的鲜血\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is covered with the blood of my friends.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.95,1:47:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我来接\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'll get it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.45,1:47:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂？你好 奥图\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hello? Oh, hello, Otto.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.41,1:47:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我读了你最新版的剧本\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I've read your last draft.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.67,1:47:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你觉得如何？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What do you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.96,1:47:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}纽约时报今天的头版 就是我的回应\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My answer is on the front page of today's New York Times.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.43,1:48:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这么讨厌啊？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You hated it that much?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.97,1:48:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}圣诞快乐 特朗勃先生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Merry Christmas, Mr. Trumbo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.61,1:48:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾德 请坐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ed, have a seat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.59,1:48:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 为什么不杀了他？- 杀啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Well, why doesn't he kill him? - Kill him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.51,1:48:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}杀了他\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Kill him!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.80,1:48:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 快杀啊 你这个蠢货 - 杀了他\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Kill him, you imbecile! - Kill him!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.26,1:48:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}杀…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Kill him!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.85,1:48:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很棒 很棒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Great. Great.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.27,1:48:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}马蒂 播放薇瑞妮亚和克拉苏那一幕\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Marty, have them put up the scene with Varinia and Crassus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.86,1:48:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 听我说 寇克 - 等一下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Listen, Kirk, I... - One second.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.49,1:49:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}华伦 我想请你发一则新闻稿\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Warren, I'd like you to put out a press release.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.74,1:49:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}该片…等等 华伦\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The screen... One second, Warren.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.46,1:49:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想到斯巴达克斯 你会想起什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What do you remember when you think about Spartacus?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.30,1:49:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他像只动物般孤身起义\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He was a man who began all alone like an animal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.18,1:49:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但他死去那天 却有千千万万人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yet on the day he died, thousands and thousands{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.26,1:49:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愿意替他而死\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would gladly have died in his place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.68,1:49:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这算什么？他是神吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What was he? Was he a god?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.81,1:49:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他不是神\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He wasn't a god.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.61,1:49:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他只是个男人 一个奴隶\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He was simple man. A slave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.24,1:49:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我爱过他\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I loved him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.37,1:49:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}华伦 新闻稿这么写\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Warren, the press release will say,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.37,1:49:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}《斯巴达克斯》由达尔顿·特朗勃编剧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"The screenplay for Spartacus was written by Dalton Trumbo."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.83,1:49:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.50,1:49:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你不解雇特朗勃 就由我来动手\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Kirk, if you don't get rid of Trumbo, I will.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.75,1:50:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那等我离开后 你可以重拍我的戏份\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And right after I quit, you can reshoot all my scenes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.47,1:50:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾德 再怎么样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You see, Ed, for better or worse,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.55,1:50:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我演的可是斯巴达克斯呢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I am Spartacus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.85,1:50:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这部电影即将上映 名叫《斯巴达克斯》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's a picture coming out. It's called Spartacus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.02,1:50:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主演 寇克·道格拉斯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's starring Kirk Douglas,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.86,1:50:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}编剧 达尔顿·特朗勃\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it is written by Dalton Trumbo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.61,1:50:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果署名是别的编剧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If there is some other writer's name on it,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.20,1:50:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请勿相信\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}don't believe it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.95,1:50:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们已经被我们看穿了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're on to them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.33,1:50:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 喂？ - 听好了 艾德\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Yes? - Now, listen, Ed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.50,1:50:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们会到所有放映的影院外抗议\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We'll picket every theater that movie is in{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.08,1:50:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}除非你今晚撤片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}unless you pull the prints tonight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.13,1:50:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并将那个叛徒的名字抹掉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And you get that traitor's name off it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.30,1:50:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赫达 别这么逼我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hedda, you can't put me in this position.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.22,1:50:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既浪费钱又没意义\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's expensive and pointless.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.47,1:50:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你和你的电影你的片厂 一起吃屎去吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Then you can kiss your movie, your studio and your miserable ass goodbye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.64,1:50:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}环球影业斥资一千二百万的《斯巴达克斯》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hollywood turns out in force to hail UI's new film spectacle, Spartacus,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.19,1:51:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}首映会上许多好莱坞名人现身力挺\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}on the premier of the $12-million picture, in the film colony.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.65,1:51:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现场的抗议人士也向我们提示着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The protesters also showed up to remind everyone of the political controversy{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.90,1:51:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本片制作期间引发的政治争议\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}surrounding the making of this film.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.13,1:52:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克莉欧？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Cleo?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.09,1:52:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了 发生什么事？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What is it? What's wrong?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.48,1:52:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一切都结束了 是吧？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's over, isn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.94,1:52:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的 没错\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes. Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.57,1:52:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们撑过来了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And we made it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.87,1:52:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.67,1:52:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯尼迪总统难得在晚上的私人时间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}President Kennedy enjoyed a rare evening off{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.34,1:52:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看了寇克·道格拉斯的新片《斯巴达克斯》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}attending the new Kirk Douglas film, Spartacus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.34,1:52:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}记者正在现场 等候总统发言\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We are here live, awaiting the president's comments.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.14,1:52:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总统先生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mr. President, Mr. President, Mr. President!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.97,1:52:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对这部颇具争议的电影\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's a very controversial film.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.81,1:52:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您有何感想？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What did you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.43,1:53:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我认为拍得很好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, I think it's a fine picture,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.27,1:53:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}应该会大卖\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and I think it's going to be a big hit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.65,1:53:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯尼迪暗示认可本片 引发广泛讨论\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The implication of Kennedy's approval of this film are wide ranging.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.78,1:53:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原著小说由前共产党员撰写\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The novel was written by a former communist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.28,1:53:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剧本也由前共产党员改编\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The screenplay was adapted by a former communist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.32,1:53:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}意味着黑名单的时代或许已经结束了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And this signifies the blacklist may be over,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.41,1:53:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寇克·道格拉斯和奥图·普莱明杰\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as Kirk Douglas and Otto Preminger{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.29,1:53:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公开宣称并挂名雇用黑名单上的编剧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}have openly hired and credited blacklisted writers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.29,1:53:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这明确批判了数十年来反共人士对艺术界的反对\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is a clear repudiation of a decade-long fight by anti-communists...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.14,1:53:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下一位得奖者\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This next award is for the member{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.85,1:53:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}提升了电影的文学境界\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}who has advanced the literature of motion pictures.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.64,1:53:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有时候 我们中间有些人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Occasionally, there appears among us a person{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.73,1:53:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}洛杉矶 1970年3月
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.48,1:53:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}牺牲小我 照亮他人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}who so subordinates his own ego to the concerns of others,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.07,1:53:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}顺应社会一切准则\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}who lives in such harmony with all the standards of the community,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.40,1:53:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并受到众人的崇敬与爱戴\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that he is revered and loved by everyone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.49,1:53:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}达尔顿·特朗勃 肯定不是这样的人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Such a man, Dalton Trumbo is not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.33,1:54:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我很荣幸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It gives me great pleasure{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.97,1:54:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}将美国编剧公会终身成就奖\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to present the Writers Guild of America Laurel Award{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.96,1:54:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}颁给达尔顿·特朗勃\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to Dalton Trumbo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.68,1:54:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恭喜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Congratulations.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.80,1:54:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢 非常感谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you, thank you very much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.06,1:54:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感谢各位女士先生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you, thank you very much, ladies and gentlemen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.52,1:54:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}通常我出席电影人聚会时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Often, when I stand before the film community,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.15,1:54:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}房里都有一只看不见的大象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there's an elephant in the room.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.03,1:54:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就是我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.62,1:54:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我想发表以下谈话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And I thought I would address that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.00,1:54:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黑名单是邪恶时代的产物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The blacklist was a time of evil.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.42,1:54:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}存活下来的人们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And no one who survived it{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.30,1:54:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无一不曾被邪恶染指\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}came through untouched by evil.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.68,1:55:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当时的情况\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Caught in a situation that had passed{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.06,1:55:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非个人能够掌控\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beyond the control of mere individuals.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.40,1:55:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而我们的行为反映了自己的天性\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Each person reacted as his nature,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.94,1:55:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}需求及信念\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}his needs, his convictions,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.90,1:55:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}眼前形势强迫我们做了某些事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and his particular circumstances compelled him to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.20,1:55:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是个恐惧的年代\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It was a time of fear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.16,1:55:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无人可以幸免\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And no one was exempt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.58,1:55:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}许多人丧失了家园\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Scores of people lost their homes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.88,1:55:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}家庭分崩离析\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Their families disintegrated. They lost!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.43,1:55:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有些人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And in some...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.69,1:55:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}甚至葬送了生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Some even lost their lives.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.65,1:55:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但当我们回顾那段黑暗时期\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But when you look back upon that dark time,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.37,1:56:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我相信我们偶尔都会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as I think you should every now and then,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.33,1:56:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}指认某人是英雄或恶人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it will do you no good{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.08,1:56:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这于事无补\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to search for heroes or villains.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.79,1:56:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们之中没有善与恶\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There weren't any.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.63,1:56:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有受害者\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There were only victims.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.97,1:56:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我们每一个人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Victims, because each of us{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:21.43,1:56:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是被强迫做出当时的言行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}felt compelled to say or do things{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.77,1:56:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}否则我们不会那么做\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that we otherwise would not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.98,1:56:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们伤害对方 或受到伤害\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To deliver or receive wounds{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.98,1:56:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但其实我们 并不想交换那些伤口\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which we truly did not wish to exchange.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.36,1:56:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在看着台下的家人们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I look out to my family sitting there,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.03,1:56:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才明白 当时害他们受了多大的苦难\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and I realize what I've put them through.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.83,1:56:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这对他们太不公平了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it's unfair.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.80,1:57:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然而我太太却成功地 维系了家庭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My wife, who somehow kept it all together,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.26,1:57:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这令我惊奇不已\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}amazes me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.77,1:57:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因此 我今晚说的这番话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And so what I say here tonight{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.52,1:57:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并不想\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is not intended{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.15,1:57:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伤害任何人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to be hurtful to anyone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.15,1:57:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而是试图治愈伤痛\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It is intended to heal the hurt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.54,1:57:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}修补多年来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To repair the wounds which, for years,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.38,1:57:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不断被撕裂的伤口\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}have been inflicted upon each other.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.97,1:57:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最糟糕的是 这些伤口已刻在我们身上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And most egregiously, upon ourselves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:48.85,1:57:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢 由衷感谢大家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you. Thank you kindly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:41.15,2:00:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若你能领取奥斯卡奖\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you receive the Oscar,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.69,2:00:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你打算做什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}what do you intend to do with it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.94,2:00:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有个女儿 今年13岁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I have... I have a daughter, 13 years old.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.62,2:00:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我从她三岁起被列入黑名单\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I've been blacklisted since she was three.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:56.62,2:00:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她知道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}She's known the title{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.58,2:01:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之后我写的每一部片子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of every motion picture I've written in this study.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.29,2:01:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而她一直保守这些秘密直到现在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And she's kept that title secret till now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:05.92,2:01:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是个战士\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A soldier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.22,2:01:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}儿时当朋友问她\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When her friends say to her, as children do,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.26,2:01:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"我爸是做这个的 你爸做什么？"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"My father does so-and-so. What does your father do?"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:14.68,2:01:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这对她而言是个头痛的问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This has confronted her with a very real problem.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:19.10,2:01:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从她三岁起一直纠缠到现在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It confronts her with the problem,\Nand has since she was three,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:22.86,2:01:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她说不出自己的父亲是谁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of who her father really is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:26.07,2:01:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以及他到底从事什么职业\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And what her father really does.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:30.70,2:01:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I, uh, think{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.24,2:01:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我能拿到那座奥斯卡 我会送给她\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I will give this Oscar, if I get it, to that girl.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:39.75,2:01:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想我会告诉她\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I think I will tell her,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:42.38,2:01:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在 这个秘密\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"Well, here is one secret{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:45.09,2:01:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不用再承担了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"you no longer need to be burdened with."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:49.30,2:01:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会告诉她 我们的名字终于又能 重见天日\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'll tell her we have our names back again.{\r}

